        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks EF for his offer of assistance. Could the viscid secretions [in glands of <hi rend="italic">Drosera</hi>] contain pepsin? Will the sodium carbonate render the testing of organic matter difficult? [See <hi rend="doubleUnderline">8979</hi>.] Will send the fluid in a fortnight.</p> 
