            <note xml:id="foot.f2">CD refers to the digestive fluid of <hi rend="italic">Drosera.</hi> See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-8979.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from Edward Frankland, 15 July 1873</ref>.</note>
